<h2>Secure, high quality and fasy delivery</h2>
<p>The three main questions we get from new customers, are regarding privacy, quality and delivery time of letters. Luckily, we have great answers to all these concerns.</p>
<p><b>Your privacy is in top</b>. Your files are stored on a secure server, all requests are encrypted with SSL and payments are made through secure gateways. Employees working at the packaging houses has signed contracts, which strictly prohibits them from accessing the content of the letters. In addition, everyone employee at LetterAmazer has signed an NDA. We do everything we can to make sure your data stays safe.</p>
<p><b>We only have quality envelopes and letters</b>. Unfortunately, the quality of the envelope and letters isn't a focus from many providers. When we send a letter, it is high quality paper (90g) and quality envelopes.</p>
<p><b>We delivery very fast</b>. We want our letters to arrive at our customers <b>FAST</b>. Therefore, we have cherry picked providers that can promise the letters arrive within days, and not weeks as many other providers do.</p>


